<h3>lazyLoad</h3>

<p>Loads cell images when a cell is selected.</p>

<p>Set the image's URL to load with <code>data-flickity-lazyload</code>.</p>

``` html
<img data-flickity-lazyload="full.jpg" />
<!-- Set optional placeholder src -->
<img src="placeholder.jpg" data-flickity-lazyload="full.jpg" />
```

<div class="example duo">
  <div class="example__code duo__cell">
    ``` js
    lazyLoad: true
    // lazyloads image in selected slide
    ```
    ``` html
    <div class="carousel">
      <div class="carousel-cell">
        <img class="carousel-cell-image"
          data-flickity-lazyload="tulip.jpg" />
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-cell">
        <img class="carousel-cell-image"
          data-flickity-lazyload="grapes.jpg" />
      </div>
      ...
    </div>
    ```
  </div>
  <div class="example__demo duo__cell">
    <div class="carousel carousel--lazyload-cells carousel--not-counting"
      data-flickity='{ "lazyLoad": true }'>
      {{> lazy-cell-images}}
    </div>
    {{> edit-demo default="vOeGzL" }}
  </div>
</div>

<p>Set <code>lazyLoad</code> to a number to load images in adjacent cells.</p>

<div class="example">
  <div class="example__code">
    ``` js
    lazyLoad: 2
    // load images in selected slide
    // and next 2 slides
    // and previous 2 slides
    ```
  </div>
  <div class="example__demo">
    <div class="carousel carousel--lazyload-adj-cells carousel--not-counting"
      data-flickity='{ "lazyLoad": 2, "initialIndex": 2 }'>
      {{> lazy-cell-images}}
    </div>
  </div>
  {{> edit-demo default="rVGLGB" }}
</div>

<p>After loading the image, Flickity will add <code>flickity-lazyloaded</code> class to the image, or <code>flickity-lazyerror</code> to a broken image. You can use this class to add a transition when images are loaded.</p>


``` css
/* fade in image when loaded */
.carousel-cell-image {
  transition: opacity 0.4s;
  opacity: 0;
}

.carousel-cell-image.flickity-lazyloaded,
.carousel-cell-image.flickity-lazyerror {
  opacity: 1;
}
```
